sequenceDiagram
%% Freeze Bridge Sequence Diagram
%% See docs/03-architecture.md §4 for full textual description
    actor User as 👤 Business User
    participant DP as Design Plane
    participant SRA as Spec Refinement Assistant
    participant VE as Validation Engine
    participant TR as Test Runner (Sandbox)
    participant RM as Release Manager
    participant RP as Runtime Plane
    participant KB as Knowledge Base

    Note over User,DP: EXPLORATION PHASE (Design Plane)
    User->>DP: NL query: "Monthly revenue by region"
    DP->>KB: Retrieve data catalog, business glossary
    DP->>User: AI-generated report preview
    User->>DP: Adjust filters, approve design
    User->>DP: Click "Freeze Workflow"

    Note over SRA,RM: FREEZE BRIDGE PHASE
    DP->>SRA: Submit AI-generated Compute Spec (YAML)
    SRA->>SRA: Scan for ambiguous nodes<br/>(inferred JOINs, fuzzy aggregations, implicit filters)
    
    alt Ambiguity found
        SRA->>User: Propose 1-3 deterministic alternatives<br/>+ confidence scores + impact analysis
        User->>SRA: Select alternative #2, confirm
    else No ambiguity
        SRA->>SRA: All nodes deterministic — fast path
    end

    SRA->>VE: Submit refined spec
    VE->>VE: Schema validation (column existence, type compatibility)
    VE->>VE: DQ Gate (data quality rules applied)
    
    alt Validation fails
        VE-->>User: Error: column mismatch, DQ threshold exceeded
        User->>DP: Return to Design Plane, fix issues
    else Validation passes
        VE->>TR: Run in Sandbox
    end

    TR->>TR: Execute with sampled data<br/>Compare output snapshot vs expected
    TR->>User: Impact Report + Test Results + Diff

    User->>RM: Approve deployment

    alt Canary enabled (Post-MVP)
        RM->>RP: Deploy 1% → monitor
        RM->>RP: Deploy 10% → monitor
        RM->>RP: Deploy 50% → monitor
        RM->>RP: Deploy 100%
    else MVP simplified flow
        RM->>RP: Deploy directly (Light Engine, deterministic)
    end

    RP->>User: Workflow live — scheduled execution begins
    RM->>User: Post-Change Summary (actual vs designed, cost profile)

    Note over User,RP: All decisions immutably recorded in audit log
